About Bangaj My work: Bangaj
This is a small and complete guest house located at South-west corner of Bangladesh. 
This guest house situated at Shyamnagor Upazila -a coastal sub-district under Satkhira district of Bangladesh and near India-Bangladesh border. 
Sundarban-UNESCO world heritage - is very close to this place.
Safe and secured for any foreigners, female, kids and even person with disabilities. It is an environment friendly best residential facilities in this area.
